xmris (4.0.5-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release (closes: #546486).
    The changes are made as follows
    + The garden data are stored under /var/lib/xmris/gardens/,
      instead of /etc/X11/app-defaults/xmris.
    + The score data are stored under /var/lib/xmris ,
      instead of /var/lib/games/xmris.
    + The 'USELOCKFILE' feature is disable.

